{
  "stem": "11290.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Naturally, from then on, our life was a living hell.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Herich Ganes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Herich Ganes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was taken to Dachau, which was not too far from Nuremberg, where the business was at that time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the family business.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would have been the fourth generation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the First World War?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they did play all the normal part that all the German Jews played in the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were, first of all, very patriotic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were convinced that Germany fought a rightful war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so my father, his brother, my mother's brothers, my mother's three brothers were all in the army, mostly in the front lines.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My uncle-- my father's brother was an officer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were both on the west and the east front of Germany, in France and in Russia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And during that time, the business was totally [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] neglected, practically non-existent, because there was nobody there but a few employees that could run it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there was no merchandise to sell anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I lived alone with my mother for four years, which I remember as a very deprived time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had very little to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we really-- the war had an enormous effect.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, only-- the only question came up, and I never had any experience about that, that [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when the war seemed to be lost, they were looking for somebody to blame.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it is always that the Jews were the natural source of blame.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they-- somebody had suggested to the Kaiser they should start counting how many Jews really served in the Army, whether they did their part.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
